  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394890/extras/38b5aae68cfce0ce0059e84b33a04b22.avif?t=1774538901\" width=128 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Amazing Tictactoe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a casual game based on 6x6 tic-tac-toe using the mouse. You can create an environment that is advantageous to you by using 4 types of items, and you win by filling 1 line with your color.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The effects of using the 4 items are as follows:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hammer: Delete a 3x3 radius centered on the mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- HandGun: Delete 5 random locations in the entire radius</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ShotGun: Delete 3 random locations in a 3x3 radius centered on the mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- WildCard: Change the designated location to your color</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394890/extras/38b5aae68cfce0ce0059e84b33a04b22.avif?t=1774538901\" width=128 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Amazing Tictactoe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a casual game based on 6x6 tic-tac-toe using the mouse. You can create an environment that is advantageous to you by using 4 types of items, and you win by filling 1 line with your color.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The effects of using the 4 items are as follows:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hammer: Delete a 3x3 radius centered on the mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- HandGun: Delete 5 random locations in the entire radius</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ShotGun: Delete 3 random locations in a 3x3 radius centered on the mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- WildCard: Change the designated location to your color</p>",
